                <h1 class="name entry-title" itemprop="itemReviewed" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Thing"><span itemprop="name">Nurse experiences of racism during Covid-19 focus of new film project</span></h1>


	<p class="post-meta">
				 <span class="tie-date"><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>06 October, 2020</span>			
						<!-- adding co-author functionality (guest authors) -->
									<span class="">By <a href="https://www.nursingtimes.net/author/megan-ford-3/" title="Posts by Megan Ford" class="author url fn" rel="author">Megan Ford</a></span>						</p>
	<div class="clear"></div>

			
